1.0.name: wordpress/toommorel-lite
1.0.description: ToomMorel Lite for WordPress is one of the easiest themes to build your Web Presence. You can get your whole website ready in just Single Click. The Theme is highly customizable and with the presence of several background patterns and Theme Options, You can have your own branded new Website for your Business or Personal Use in Minutes. Features Templates for Blogs, Gallery, Fullwidth Page without sidebar and Contact Us Page.
